tosdr.case: The service can sell or otherwise transfer your personal data as part of a bankruptcy proceeding or other type of financial transaction.

title: The service can sell or otherwise transfer your personal data as part of a bankruptcy proceeding or other type of financial transaction.
quoteText:
We may have to share your personal data with the parties set out below for the purposes set out in paragraph 4 above.

  • Internal Third Parties as set out in the Glossary.
  • External Third Parties as set out in the Glossary.
  • Third parties to whom we may choose to sell, transfer, or merge parts of our business or our assets. or who may be interested in buying our business or investing.
